353
00:13:26,974 --> 00:13:28,984
The tale of Barney Stinson,

354
00:13:29,009 --> 00:13:31,039
Player King of New York City.

355
00:13:36,549 --> 00:13:39,389
Once upon a time, we all
went out to get our drink on.

356
00:13:39,419 --> 00:13:41,119
When who should
walk in but a girl

357
