360
00:13:46,559 --> 00:13:48,729
As Barney put it,
oh so eloquently:

361
00:13:48,761 --> 00:13:50,561
Boy-oy-oy-oing.

362
00:13:50,597 --> 00:13:53,997
He rose to go approach this
girl commanding such intrigue

363
